# Place your images in this folder

Image naming convention:
- product-1.jpg, product-2.jpg, etc. for product images
- product-1-alt.jpg for alternative product images
- about-preview.jpg for about section
- company-overview.jpg for company overview
- placeholder.jpg for fallback images

Recommended image sizes:
- Product images: 400x300px (4:3 ratio)
- Hero images: 1920x600px
- Gallery thumbnails: 80x80px
